      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare find for the collector or enthusiast, maintained in true museum-quality condition. The exterior paint retains a breathtaking, mirror-like depth, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns with factory precision. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain supple and entirely free of wear bolsters, still retaining that distinct 'new car' aroma. All high-tech amenities, including the panoramic interface and premium surround sound, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified technicians with a full paper trail of maintenance. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine, turn-key example of automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
